{"tid":1789100,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Star Wars 星球大戰：天行者的崛起 劣評如潮！！連Fans都屌到塌皮！","createTime":"2019-12-19T08:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T16:02:26.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"080530371f55e14697651734dfd95b5d2cf1c25e","tid":1789100,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcjcUjJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcjcUjJ.png&h=b56591fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7oMe7EZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7oMe7EZ.png&h=9a38e1ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dc33dc8b9d9a839940518c87fedf11c25284a61","tid":1789100,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"慘遭滑鐵盧？《星際大戰 Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker》首波評分表現出爐<br />\n<br />\n「爛番茄」評分僅有 56%，你們怎麼看？<br />\n<br />\n象徵《Star Wars》系列電影新三部曲的傳奇最終章《Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker》於昨日正式上映，相信不少星戰迷都早已訂票於首日衝進戲院觀賞。<br />\n<br />\n本集再次邀請 J.J. Abrams 回歸執導劃下新句點，過去的第七集與第八集（Rian Johnson 執導）的評價都算是兩極，支持者與擁護者都各持己見地具有自己的觀點，不過對星戰迷來說，批評歸批評，但仍會購票進戲院觀看，而今番 Rotten Tomatoes 亦捎來了首日的評分表現：56%（117 則評分）；另一邊 IMDb 之 Metacritic 部分則是 53 分（32 則專業評分），目前看起來表現有待加強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/12/star-wars-the-rise-of-skywalker-rotten-tomatoes-metacritic-review\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2019%2F12%2Fstar-wars-the-rise-of-skywalker-rotten-tomatoes-metacritic-review&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=899307c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/12/star-wars-the-rise-of-skywalker-rotten-tomatoes-metacritic-review</a>"},{"pid":"411a3340e98ec7731a29d251939e588fd04163f6","tid":1789100,"uid":157304,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"J.J. Abrams要執返EP8嘅屎，等於一集要講兩集嘅嘢，拍到咁樣算係咁&hellip;&hellip;"},{"